luwa-ul
================================================

Version: 1.0.1
Date: 2025-10-26
Author: Kosei Kawaguchi a.k.a. KKTeX
License: LPPL 1.3c

Description:
------------
This package provides underlining and highlighting that remain intact even in vertical writing environments and when used together with ruby text.

Dependencies:
-------------
luacolor, xcolor, lua-ul, calc, tikz

Notice
This package is **LuaLaTeX-only**. 

See luwa-ul-doc.tex for usage examples.